TY  - JOUR
TI  - Simultaneous Price and Quantity Adjustment in a Single Market
AU  - Beckmann, Martin J.
AU  - Ryder, Harl E.
AB  - [This paper discusses the dynamics of disequilibrium in a single market where both price and quantity change in response to disequilibrium. We describe the nature of the adjustment path under a wide variety of assumptions, noting in particular the properties of stability in the large and in the small and the existence of limit cycles.]
